name: New And Better Edelgard van Hresvleg V2 Fire Emblem
description:
Hi i learned alot about Loras so here is a new and much better version of the edelgard Lora, the old one was trained on 3000 danbooru images, this one was created using 100 handpicked images and tagging them accordingly.

Best to use at 0.7 weight

To use the model best use:

Edelgard Emperor:

Use (Edelgard Emperor) in the positive prompt

Normal Edelgard:

Use (Edelgard van Hresvle) in the positive prompt and use Edelgard Emperor in the negative prompt

Monastery Edelgard:

Use (Edelgard van Hresvle) and (garreg mach monastery uniform, black uniform) in the positive prompt and use Edelgard Emperor in the negative prompt

modelVersions.name: Edelgard van Hresvleg V3
modelVersions.description:
Changed a lot of things thanks to this guide, is now even better then version V2:

https://rentry.org/LazyTrainingGuide

Best to use at 0.65 weight

Outfits

Edelgard Emperor:

Use (Edelgard Emperor) in the positive prompt

Normal Edelgard:

Use (Edelgard van Hresvle) in the positive prompt and !!!use (Edelgard Emperor) in the negative prompt

Monastery Edelgard:

Use (Edelgard van Hresvleg) and (garreg mach monastery uniform, black uniform) in the positive prompt and !!!use (Edelgard Emperor) in the negative prompt

I would recommend using the prompt upper body for best results

All images were created using Anything V4.5
